# Instructions for writing a test:
#
# t: initializes new test
# n: initializes bit array
# r: rotates bit array subset at offset, length by amount
# e: expects raw bit array value

# Ex:
# t 0
# 
# n 10010110
# r 0 8 -1
# e 00101101

# Place your 20 test cases below, here.
# ==========================================
# 边界极限测试 (Boundary & Edge Cases)
# ==========================================

# 3: Zero length (长度为0，数组不应发生任何改变)
t 3
n 11001100
r 2 0 5
e 11001100

# 4: Zero shift amount (旋转步数为0，不应改变)
t 4
n 10101010
r 0 8 0
e 10101010

# 5: Shift exactly equal to length (右旋步数等于长度，等同于不转)
t 5
n 11110000
r 0 8 8
e 11110000

# 6: Negative shift exactly equal to length (左旋步数等于长度，等同于不转)
t 6
n 00001111
r 0 8 -8
e 00001111

# 7: Shift amount is a large multiple of length (大倍数取模，16 % 8 = 0)
t 7
n 10000001
r 0 8 16
e 10000001

# 8: Subset length is 1 (子数组长度仅为1，无论怎么转都不变)
t 8
n 01010101
r 3 1 5
e 01010101

# ==========================================
# 局部子数组偏移测试 (Subset Offset Cases)
# ==========================================

# 9: Subset strictly at the beginning (仅旋转头部)
t 9
n 10001111
r 0 4 1
e 01001111

# 10: Subset strictly at the end (仅旋转尾部，负数左旋)
t 10
n 11110001
r 4 4 -1
e 11110010

# 11: Subset in the exact middle crossing byte boundary (跨越字节边界的中间旋转)
t 11
n 1111100000011111
r 4 8 2
e 1111011000001111

# ==========================================
# 复杂的取模与不对称测试 (Modulo & Asymmetric)
# ==========================================

# 12: Positive shift larger than length (正数大步数截断：5 % 4 = 1)
t 12
n 10101010
r 2 4 5
e 10010110

# 13: Negative shift larger than length (负数大步数截断：-7 左旋等同于右旋 1 步)
t 13
n 11001100
r 0 4 -7
e 01101100

# 14: Shift by length minus one right (右移 长度-1，等同于左移 1 步)
t 14
n 10000000
r 0 8 7
e 00000001

# 15: Shift by length minus one left (左移 长度-1，等同于右移 1 步)
t 15
n 00000001
r 0 8 -7
e 10000000

# 16: Asymmetric split (奇数长度的非对称旋转)
t 16
n 11100001
r 0 7 3
e 00011101

# 17: Non-byte aligned offset and length (极其刁钻的非字节对齐切片)
t 17
n 11011011
r 1 6 -2
e 11101101

# ==========================================
# 特殊位模式 (Special Bit Patterns)
# ==========================================

# 18: All 1s (全1防呆测试)
t 18
n 11111111
r 2 4 -3
e 11111111

# 19: All 0s (全0防呆测试)
t 19
n 00000000
r 1 6 2
e 00000000

# ==========================================
# 复合与长数据测试 (Consecutive & Long Data)
# ==========================================

# 20: Large bit array across 3 bytes (24 bits) 
# t 20
# n 111100001010101000001111
# r 4 16 4
# e 111100000000101010101111

# 21: Consecutive crazy operations on the same array (同一数组的疯狂连招)
t 21
n 10010110
r 0 8 1
e 01001011
r 2 4 -1
e 01010011
r 0 8 0
e 01010011
r 0 4 8
e 01010011

# 22: Very large shift on whole block (超大数值取模测试)
t 22
n 10000000
r 0 8 100001
e 01000000


